This paper deals with improving query execution in databases, which is a core topic in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the implementation of a runtime code generation engine, which involves programming languages and compilers (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the integration of this engine into an existing database system, which involves software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the performance improvements achieved through this approach, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CR).
